{"tid":2389560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙祠取消公眾上頭炷香儀式 近百年來首次","createTime":"2021-02-01T04:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T07:17:39.000Z","uid":24660,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"877f698cd16bd506961c9a8856cf63c0a9a1ca9b","tid":2389560,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"每年農曆年三十晚，不少善信都會到黃大仙祠上頭炷香，受武漢肺炎疫情影響，嗇色園宣佈取消年三十晚公眾入園上頭炷香的儀式，屬嗇色園創立近百年以來首次。黃大仙祠監院李耀輝（義覺道長）表示，當晚將會封園，公眾、傳媒未能入內，將由香港電台直播子夜上香的情況，而嗇色園亦會直播儀式。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/THJTHKCG6JBIDE5RGRMXSGXB5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FTHJTHKCG6JBIDE5RGRMXSGXB5A%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1Gy8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=27d45336\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FTHJTHKCG6JBIDE5RGRMXSGXB5A%2F&h=45ef6c57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/THJTHKCG6JBIDE5RGRMXSGXB5A/</a>"},{"pid":"f4d22b323813764468136b1b94c5ff751054c2eb","tid":2389560,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"咁車公呢？ 佢好似主打抗疫"},{"pid":"1608aa83b71c54d1aa640bdd02a4f686134dc232","tid":2389560,"uid":195248,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"夏惠姨今年...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46d96a2bb898f5bb681de9bf6cda4d8ebdbbfa5","tid":2389560,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"算把啦 荷蘭叻都係道長 都唔會再添香油比佢"},{"pid":"7548b13eabc7336cbb49b09b94984c2d314b1881","tid":2389560,"uid":33730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"無得睇夏惠姨扮牛牛上頭炷香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760e4258c17b61ad8d3e895c90c2e0045b5543f7",